    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The reason for this is that we don't have the state to compute the proof ourselves when we are in forking mode.\r\n\r\nso as soon as we mined the first block, there's no easy/cheap way to compute it.\r\n\r\nwe could delegate the getProof call if we're still on the mined block however",
